<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
<title>Phoenix, AZ Plumbing Market Intelligence Brief — Plumbing & HVAC SEO</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --brand:      #B6D872;
  --brand-dark: #8AB045;
  --ink:        #3D3D3D;
  --ink-deep:   #1A1A1A;
  --ink-mid:    #6B6B6B;
  --paper:      #F2F2F2;
  --white:      #FFFFFF;
  --rule:       #E2E2E2;
  --mist:       #F4F4F2;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink-deep);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;}

/* ── COVER ── */
.cover{background:var(--ink);min-height:100vh;display:grid;grid-template-rows:auto 1fr auto;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.cover::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg,transparent,transparent 40px,rgba(180,214,111,0.05) 40px,rgba(180,214,111,0.05) 41px);}
.cover::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:4px;background:var(--brand);}
.cover-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:2.5rem 4rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);position:relative;z-index:1;}
.cover-badge{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:0.7rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);padding:.4rem .8rem;border-radius:2px;}
.cover-body{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:4rem;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.cover-eyebrow{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--brand);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;}
.cover-eyebrow::after{content:'';width:3rem;height:1px;background:var(--brand);}
.cover-title{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(3.5rem,8vw,7.5rem);color:var(--white);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:.01em;max-width:900px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.cover-title em{color:var(--brand);font-style:normal;}
.cover-subtitle{font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);font-weight:300;max-width:540px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:3.5rem;}
.cover-stats{display:flex;gap:3rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.cover-stat{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:.25rem;}
.cover-stat-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2.4rem;color:var(--white);line-height:1;}
.cover-stat-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.65rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;}
.cover-footer{padding:2rem 4rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.cover-footer-note{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.65rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);letter-spacing:.1em;}

/* ── LAYOUT ── */
.report-body{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 4rem;}
.divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--rule);margin:5rem 0;}

/* ── TYPE ── */
.section-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--brand-dark);margin-bottom:.75rem;}
.section-title{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2.8rem;letter-spacing:.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--ink-deep);margin-bottom:1.25rem;}
.section-intro{font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--ink-mid);max-width:640px;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:300;}

/* ── EXEC SUMMARY ── */
.exec-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:1.5px;background:var(--rule);border:1.5px solid var(--rule);margin-bottom:4rem;}
.exec-card{background:var(--white);padding:2rem 1.75rem;position:relative;}
.exec-card.highlight{background:var(--ink-deep);}
.exec-card.highlight .exec-num{color:var(--brand);}
.exec-card.highlight .exec-label{color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);}
.exec-card.highlight .exec-desc{color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);}
.exec-card.accent{background:var(--brand);} 
.exec-card.accent .exec-num{color:var(--ink-deep);}
.exec-card.accent .exec-label{color:rgba(0,0,0,.5);}
.exec-card.accent .exec-desc{color:rgba(0,0,0,.7);}
.exec-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:3.5rem;line-height:1;color:var(--brand);margin-bottom:.25rem;}
.exec-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35);margin-bottom:.75rem;}
.exec-desc{font-size:.88rem;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.6;}

/* ── REVENUE SECTION ── */
.rev-callout{background:var(--ink-deep);padding:3.5rem;margin:2rem 0 3rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.rev-callout::before{content:'$';position:absolute;right:-1rem;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:18rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.03);line-height:1;}
.rev-big{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem);color:var(--brand);line-height:1;margin-bottom:.5rem;}
.rev-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.7rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:2rem;}
.rev-desc{font-size:1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);max-width:580px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.75;}
.rev-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1.5px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin-top:2.5rem;}
.rev-cell{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);padding:1.5rem 1.25rem;}
.rev-cell-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.2rem;}
.rev-cell-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.62rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1.4;}

/* ── MARKET SHARE ── */
.market-share-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;margin-bottom:3rem;}
.donut-wrap{position:relative;width:240px;height:240px;margin:0 auto;}
.donut-wrap svg{width:100%;height:100%;}
.donut-center{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);text-align:center;}
.donut-pct{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2.8rem;color:var(--ink-deep);line-height:1;}
.donut-sub{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.6rem;color:var(--ink-mid);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;}
.market-legend{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;}
.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;}
.legend-dot{width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0;}
.legend-company{font-size:.9rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink-deep);}
.legend-pct{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--ink-mid);margin-left:auto;}
.concentration-bar{margin-top:2rem;}
.conc-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-mid);margin-bottom:.75rem;}
.bar-track{height:12px;background:var(--rule);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;display:flex;}
.bar-seg{height:100%;transition:width .3s;}
.bar-legend{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;margin-top:.75rem;}
.bar-leg-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.4rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.62rem;color:var(--ink-mid);}
.bar-leg-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:1px;}
.market-statement{background:var(--mist);border-left:3px solid var(--brand);padding:1.5rem 2rem;margin-top:2rem;font-size:1rem;color:var(--ink-deep);font-weight:500;line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;}

/* ── CONVERSION LEAKAGE ── */
.leak-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5px;background:var(--rule);border:1.5px solid var(--rule);margin-bottom:2.5rem;}
.leak-card{background:var(--white);padding:1.75rem;}
.leak-icon{font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:.75rem;}
.leak-feature{font-weight:600;font-size:.92rem;color:var(--ink-deep);margin-bottom:.25rem;}
.leak-stat{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2rem;color:var(--brand);line-height:1;margin-bottom:.25rem;}
.leak-stat.danger{color:#C0392B;}
.leak-desc{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.55;}
.leak-math{background:var(--ink-deep);padding:2rem 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;margin-top:0;}
.leak-math-cell{text-align:center;}
.leak-math-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--white);line-height:1;}
.leak-math-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.6rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:.25rem;line-height:1.4;}
.leak-math-op{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2rem;color:var(--brand);text-align:center;}
.leak-statement{margin-top:2rem;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-deep);text-align:center;letter-spacing:-.01em;}

/* ── 90-DAY WINDOW ── */
.window-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.5px;background:var(--rule);border:1.5px solid var(--rule);margin-bottom:2.5rem;}
.window-card{background:var(--white);padding:2rem 1.75rem;}
.window-card.dark{background:var(--ink-deep);}
.window-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:4rem;color:var(--brand);line-height:.9;margin-bottom:.5rem;}
.window-title{font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--ink-deep);margin-bottom:.5rem;}
.window-card.dark .window-title{color:var(--white);}
.window-body{font-size:.88rem;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.65;}
.window-card.dark .window-body{color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);}
.window-terms{margin-top:2rem;}
.term-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;padding:.85rem 1.25rem;background:var(--white);border-left:3px solid transparent;margin-bottom:1.5px;}
.term-row.open{border-left-color:var(--brand);}
.term-row.contested{border-left-color:var(--ink-mid);}
.term-row.locked{border-left-color:var(--rule);}
.term-name{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--ink-deep);flex:1;}
.term-status{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.25rem .6rem;border-radius:2px;}
.status-open{background:#EEF6DC;color:#6FA832;}
.status-contested{background:#FFF8E1;color:#B7791F;}
.status-locked{background:#F5F5F5;color:#9B9B9B;}
.window-cta{background:var(--brand);padding:2rem 2.5rem;margin-top:0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
.window-cta-text{font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-deep);max-width:500px;line-height:1.5;}
.window-cta-badge{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-deep);opacity:.7;white-space:nowrap;}

/* ── KEYWORD RANKINGS ── */
.keyword-block{margin-bottom:3rem;}
.keyword-term{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.keyword-tag{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.8rem;background:var(--ink-deep);color:var(--white);padding:.35rem .75rem;}
.keyword-volume{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.7rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35);letter-spacing:.1em;}
.rank-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;}
.rank-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2rem 1fr auto auto;align-items:center;gap:1rem;padding:.9rem 1.25rem;background:var(--white);border-left:3px solid transparent;}
.rank-item.pos-1{border-left-color:var(--brand);}
.rank-item.map-pack{background:#F4FAE8;border-left-color:var(--brand);}
.rank-pos{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.4rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.2);text-align:center;}
.rank-item.pos-1 .rank-pos,.rank-item.map-pack .rank-pos{color:var(--brand-dark);}
.rank-company{font-weight:500;font-size:.92rem;}
.rank-url{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.7rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35);}
.rank-type{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:.25rem .6rem;border-radius:2px;white-space:nowrap;}
.type-organic{background:#EEF2FF;color:#3730A3;}
.type-maps{background:#EEF6DC;color:#6FA832;}
.type-paid{background:#FEF3C7;color:#B7791F;}
.rank-score{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.75rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35);}

/* ── SCORECARD ── */
.scorecard-wrap{overflow-x:auto;border:1.5px solid var(--rule);}
.scorecard{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.85rem;}
.scorecard thead tr{background:var(--ink-deep);}
.scorecard th{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-align:left;font-weight:400;white-space:nowrap;}
.scorecard td{padding:.85rem 1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);vertical-align:middle;}
.scorecard tbody tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
.scorecard tbody tr:nth-child(even) td{background:var(--mist);}
.co-name{font-weight:600;font-size:.88rem;}
.co-url{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.68rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35);display:block;margin-top:2px;}
.badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.62rem;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:2px;white-space:nowrap;}
.badge-yes{background:#EEF6DC;color:#6FA832;}
.badge-no{background:#FEE2E2;color:#991B1B;}
.badge-partial{background:#FEF3C7;color:#B7791F;}
.traffic-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;}
.traffic-fill{height:6px;background:var(--brand);border-radius:2px;min-width:4px;}
.traffic-label{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.68rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.4);white-space:nowrap;}
.opportunity-flag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.35rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.62rem;color:#6FA832;letter-spacing:.08em;font-weight:500;}
.opportunity-flag::before{content:'▲';font-size:.5rem;}

/* ── FINDINGS ── */
.findings-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:start;}
.finding-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--brand-dark);margin-bottom:.75rem;}
.finding-title{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:.75rem;line-height:1.1;color:var(--ink-deep);}
.finding-body{font-size:.92rem;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.75;font-weight:300;}

/* ── CTA ── */
.cta-section{background:var(--brand);padding:5rem 4rem;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.cta-section::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,transparent,transparent 30px,rgba(0,0,0,.04) 30px,rgba(0,0,0,.04) 31px);}
.cta-title{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.5rem);color:var(--ink-deep);line-height:.95;margin-bottom:1.25rem;position:relative;}
.cta-body{font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.6);max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;position:relative;}
.cta-phone{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--ink-deep);letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:2.5rem;position:relative;font-weight:500;}
.cta-btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--ink-deep);color:var(--white);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.8rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:1rem 2.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;position:relative;transition:transform .15s;}
.cta-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
.report-footer{background:var(--ink-deep);padding:2.5rem 4rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
.footer-note{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:.62rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);letter-spacing:.1em;}

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
.cover-eyebrow{animation:fadeUp .6s .1s both;}
.cover-title{animation:fadeUp .6s .2s both;}
.cover-subtitle{animation:fadeUp .6s .3s both;}
.cover-stats{animation:fadeUp .6s .4s both;}

@media(max-width:768px){
  .cover-header,.cover-body,.cover-footer,.report-body,.cta-section,.report-footer{padding:2rem;}
  .exec-grid,.leak-grid,.window-grid,.findings-grid,.market-share-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .rev-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .leak-math{grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;gap:.5rem;padding:1.5rem 1rem;}
  .leak-math-num{font-size:1.4rem;}
  .leak-math-op{font-size:1.4rem;}
  .leak-math-label{font-size:.55rem;}
  .scorecard-wrap{-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;}
  .scorecard{min-width:700px;}
  .rank-item{grid-template-columns:1.5rem 1fr auto;}
  .rank-score{display:none;}
  .window-cta{flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;text-align:center;}
  .cover-title{font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem);}
  .section-title{font-size:2rem;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- COVER -->
<section class="cover">
  <header class="cover-header">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," style="height:38px;" alt="Plumbing &amp; HVAC SEO">
    <div class="cover-badge">Confidential Market Intelligence Brief</div>
  </header>
  <div class="cover-body">
    <div class="cover-eyebrow">Phoenix, AZ &middot; Plumbing Industry &middot; March 2026</div>
    <h1 class="cover-title">Phoenix's Plumbing Market: <em>Who Wins the Digital Revenue</em></h1>
    <p class="cover-subtitle">15 competitors analyzed. 8 keywords tracked. What the Map Pack and organic rankings reveal about who's actually capturing the high-intent calls.</p>
    <div class="cover-stats">
      <div class="cover-stat"><div class="cover-stat-num">15</div><div class="cover-stat-label">Companies Analyzed</div></div>
      <div class="cover-stat"><div class="cover-stat-num">8</div><div class="cover-stat-label">Keywords Tracked</div></div>
      <div class="cover-stat"><div class="cover-stat-num">7</div><div class="cover-stat-label">Open Opportunities</div></div>
      <div class="cover-stat"><div class="cover-stat-num">$860K</div><div class="cover-stat-label">Est. Monthly Market Revenue</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="cover-footer">
    <div class="cover-footer-note">PREPARED BY PLUMBING &amp; HVAC SEO &middot; PLUMBERSEO.NET</div>
    <div class="cover-footer-note">866-610-4647 &middot; CONFIDENTIAL</div>
  </footer>
</section>

<!-- REPORT BODY -->
<main class="report-body">

<!-- ═══ EXECUTIVE SUMMARY ═══ -->
<div class="section-label">Executive Summary</div>
<h2 class="section-title">A Consolidating Market, But Not Yet Locked</h2>
<p class="section-intro">Phoenix's plumbing market generates roughly $860K in monthly revenue flowing through digital search. That revenue is being concentrated in the hands of three companies — but the secondary terms and Map Pack positions are still contestable for the next 60–90 days.</p>

<div class="exec-grid">
  <div class="exec-card highlight">
    <div class="exec-num">$860K</div>
    <div class="exec-label">Estimated monthly revenue from digital search</div>
    <div class="exec-desc">Based on 21,870 monthly high-intent searches, a 35% click-to-call rate, 25% booking conversion, and an $450 average ticket. Three companies currently capture the majority of this revenue.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="exec-card">
    <div class="exec-num">3</div>
    <div class="exec-label">Dominant players control visibility</div>
    <div class="exec-desc">Parker &amp; Sons, The Aussie Plumber, and Maloney Plumbing &amp; Drain Services hold the top positions on primary terms. Their combined digital advantage is built on years of review accumulation and GBP investment.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="exec-card">
    <div class="exec-num">7</div>
    <div class="exec-label">High-reputation operators invisible online</div>
    <div class="exec-desc">Seven companies in this analysis have 4.9–5.0 star ratings with hundreds of verified reviews — and virtually no digital visibility. Proven operators losing revenue daily to companies with stronger online infrastructure.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="exec-card accent">
    <div class="exec-num">60–90</div>
    <div class="exec-label">Days to shift Map Pack on secondary terms</div>
    <div class="exec-desc">Water heater repair, drain cleaning, and emergency plumbing have open Map Pack positions. Strategic GBP investment and review velocity can move rankings within one quarter.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="exec-card">
    <div class="exec-num">68%</div>
    <div class="exec-label">Of competitors lack online booking infrastructure</div>
    <div class="exec-desc">Most Phoenix plumbers have no integrated scheduling system. Every friction point between prospect and appointment is a lead that goes to whoever made it easiest to book.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="exec-card">
    <div class="exec-num">35%</div>
    <div class="exec-label">Estimated click-to-call conversion rate</div>
    <div class="exec-desc">This is the actual traffic that gets dialed. The ability to convert that call into a booked job depends on response speed, availability visibility, and how frictionless the booking experience is.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="divider">

<!-- ═══ REVENUE OPPORTUNITY ═══ -->
<div class="section-label">Section 01 &mdash; Revenue Opportunity Snapshot</div>
<h2 class="section-title">How Revenue Is Being Allocated</h2>
<p class="section-intro">Search engines function as a revenue distribution mechanism. In Phoenix, roughly 21,870 high-intent plumbing searches occur every month. Where that traffic lands determines who gets the call.</p>

<div class="rev-callout">
  <div class="rev-big">$860,850</div>
  <div class="rev-label">Estimated Monthly Revenue Flowing Through Digital Search &mdash; Phoenix Plumbing Market</div>
  <div class="rev-desc">This figure is conservative and based on real search volume data. It assumes a 35% click-to-call rate on captured traffic, 25% booking conversion, and a $450 average ticket. Estimated based on stated assumptions.</div>
  <div class="rev-grid">
    <div class="rev-cell">
      <div class="rev-cell-num">21,870</div>
      <div class="rev-cell-label">Monthly high-intent searches across tracked terms</div>
    </div>
    <div class="rev-cell">
      <div class="rev-cell-num">35%</div>
