    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.75;max-width:680px;margin-bottom:1rem;"><strong>Formula:</strong> 21,870 searches × 35% CTR × 25% conversion × $450 ticket = $860,850 monthly estimated revenue. Estimated based on stated assumptions. The critical insight is not the total market size — it is the concentration. Three operators are capturing the disproportionate share of this revenue today. That concentration was built through sustained digital investment, not through superior service delivery alone.</p>

