<!-- ═══ CONVERSION LEAKAGE ═══ -->
<div class="section-label">Section 03 &mdash; Conversion Friction &amp; Lead Leakage</div>
<h2 class="section-title">Visibility Is Only Half the Problem</h2>
<p class="section-intro">Getting found is step one. Converting that visit into a booked job is where most Phoenix plumbers lose the revenue they worked to earn. The data is clear: friction kills the lead.</p>

<div class="leak-grid">
  <div class="leak-card">
