    <div class="leak-stat danger">68%</div>
    <div class="leak-desc">of Phoenix plumbers have no online booking. In 2026, a homeowner with a burst pipe at 9pm will book whoever answers digitally — not whoever they have to call back tomorrow.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="leak-card">
    <div class="leak-icon">💬</div>
    <div class="leak-feature">Live Chat / 2-Way SMS</div>
    <div class="leak-stat danger">60%</div>
    <div class="leak-desc">lack any real-time communication option. The companies winning conversions — Parker &amp; Sons, Maloney, Benjamin Franklin — all offer instant response pathways. Speed converts the lead.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="leak-card">
    <div class="leak-icon">⭐</div>
    <div class="leak-feature">Review Velocity Gap</div>
    <div class="leak-stat">3,200</div>
    <div class="leak-desc">average reviews among mid-tier operators vs. 32,563 for Parker &amp; Sons. That review concentration directly suppresses Map Pack ranking for everyone else.</div>
  </div>
</div>

